name: ElsaHouseKeeper
0:
”Alexa, tell housekeeper elsa to remember that car key was kept on dresser”
”Alexa, ask housekeeper elsa where is the car key”
”Alexa, tell housekeeper elsa to forget car key”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: housekeeper elsa
des: Tell Elsa to remember things which other person in your house may need when you are not around. For example car key is kept on dresser. When you are not around your spouse can ask Elsa to know where you kept your car key!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
